    "intro": "Interpretation asks what the text means — moving from observation to the author's intent in its canonical and historical context. The movements below trace the psalm's argument through its two stanzas, its grounding theology, and its culminating covenant claim. Where the original Hebrew sharpens the English, a brief note supplements the exposition.",
